# Portal Feature Audit & UI Hardening - Verification Complete

All Portal features have been verified and are fully functional.

## Verified Features

### 1. "Librarian" Visual Pivot (Aesthetic Overhaul)
The UI has been completely refreshed to match the "Librarian Visual Intelligence" design system.

![Librarian Aesthetic](file:///Users/base/.gemini/antigravity/brain/96534431-eec5-45ce-b60c-0118b51f4eb0/librarian_aesthetic_proof_final_1767532421302.png)

- **Deep Navy Background**: `#06090F` providing a high-contrast, professional "dark mode" canvas.
- **Emerald Green Accents**: Vibrant `#10B981` buttons and status indicators for clear calls to action.
- **Refined Card Layout**: Dark, subtle cards with clear metadata hierarchy and platform tagging.

### 2. Single Page Consolidation
- **Zero Sidebar**: A clean, full-width vertical feed.
- **Glassmorphism Header**: Sticky header with search and ingest controls, using background blur for depth.
- **Activity Banner**: Auto-hiding banner that mimics dashboard widgets (only visible when active).

### 3. Settings Modal (Fixed UX)
The settings panel is now an overlay modal with clear language and visual hierarchy.

![Settings Modal](file:///Users/base/.gemini/antigravity/brain/96534431-eec5-45ce-b60c-0118b51f4eb0/fixed_settings_aesthetic_1767531825971.png)

- **Clarified Fields**: "Local Network Access" with LAN badge (replacing cryptic IP labels).
- **Help Text**: Added context descriptions for all configuration options.
- **Maintenance Tools**: Clearly labeled buttons for "Sync Library" and "Fix Thumbnails".

