## Summary
The "SAAS demonspawn" UI has been successfully eliminated. The Portal now embodies the "Librarian" aesthetic: **Clean. Dark. Data-First.**

- ✅ **Aesthetic**: Deep Navy + Emerald Green + Glassmorphism.
- ✅ **Layout**: Single Page, No Sidebar, Modal Settings.
- ✅ **UX**: Clarified labels, auto-hiding activity, responsive grid.
